	<section class='even'>
		<div class='container'>
			<div class='row-wrapper' id='products-services'>
				<div class='row'>
					<h3>Products</h3>
					<span class='desc'>
						Iris Dynamics currently offers three products. The Bumblebee Control Loading Yoke is our low-cost
						consumer product.  The Dragonfly Control Loading Yoke serves the global prosumer flight simulator market.
						The EmZ Control Loading Module is our commercial-off-the-Shelf (COTS) product which uses our core
						technology to military and civilian system integrators.
					</span>
					<div class='col-md-12 products'>
						<%= render 'shared/catalog' %>
					</div>
					<div class='col-md-6'>
						<h4>Consulting and Custom Solutions</h4>
						<span class='desc'>
							Iris Dynamics offers consulting services and development of specialized solutions and technology
							transfer for the defence, aviation, heavy equipment, automotive, marine, robotic, undersea, and
							other applications. The IRIS Dynamics EmZ Technology can be customized for a variety of host
							systems and is ideal for system integrators.  The company will also undertake custom engineering
							projects by applying our unique, value-added hardware, software, and integration services to
							deliver industry-specific motion control solutions.
						</span>
					</div>
					<div class='col-md-6'>
						<h4>Research and Development</h4>
						<span class='desc'>
							Research & Development is at the heart of Iris Dynamics. Our continued R&D initiatives allow us
							to provide innovative, state-of-the-art, yet proven products and systems to industry.  We work
							closely with Universities, key customers and the Aerospace industry to apply our innovative
							technology to new motion control challenges.
						</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

