						</p>
						<p>
							IRIS Dynamics is a secure and trusted company that holds appropriate security clearances and is
							registered with the Canadian Controlled Goods Program and an active member of CADSI.
						</p>
						<p>
							IRIS Dynamics started as a successful Kickstarter campaign in 2013 to develop a new kind of
							control-loading flight yoke for flight simulation. Since then the technology has scaled and
							evolved into a variety of other applications.
							OUR MISSION: We are the advanced motion control systems innovator that provides precision
							control-loading actuator systems for aerial, marine and terrestrial vehicles, factory automation,
							simulation and remote control.
						</p>
						<p>
